  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operation Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>DBR Systems Pte Ltd is a Singapore SME registered in 2012. We provide a one-stop supply of printers’ ink and toner cartridges, imaging (drum) units, printer ribbons, UPS, data storage media, and IT-related peripherals.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will manage the preparation and dispatch of outgoing items, coordinate transportation and storage activities, support inventory management, and maintain a clean and organized work environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Issue, pack, seal, and label outgoing items accurately to ensure correct delivery</li><li>Organize transportation activities by managing storage, tracking movement of goods from origin to delivery, and arranging necessary transport services</li><li>Inspect items to confirm they are undamaged before dispatch</li><li>Collaborate with the Senior Manager to restock products based on operational needs</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and orderliness of the work area to support a safe and efficient environment</li><li>Participate in scheduled stock takes to verify inventory accuracy</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned to support team operations</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Hold a valid Class 3 driving license</li></ul>",
